## [TAILWIND-FORMS]

### Контейнер формы
```css
.space-y-6  /* для основных форм */
.space-y-4  /* для компактных форм */
```

### Поле формы (label + input)
```css
/* Label */
.block.text-sm.font-medium.text-gray-700.dark:text-gray-300.mb-2

/* Обязательное поле (звездочка) */
.text-red-500

/* Input (текст, email, number, date, time, datetime-local) */
.w-full.px-3.py-2.border.border-gray-300.dark:border-gray-600.rounded-md.shadow-sm
.focus:outline-none.focus:ring-2.focus:ring-blue-500.focus:border-blue-500
.dark:bg-gray-700.dark:text-white

/* Textarea */
.w-full.px-3.py-2.border.border-gray-300.dark:border-gray-600.rounded-md.shadow-sm
.focus:outline-none.focus:ring-2.focus:ring-blue-500.focus:border-blue-500
.dark:bg-gray-700.dark:text-white
.rows-4  /* или другое количество строк */

/* Select (dropdown) */
.w-full.px-3.py-2.border.border-gray-300.dark:border-gray-600.rounded-md.shadow-sm
.focus:outline-none.focus:ring-2.focus:ring-blue-500.focus:border-blue-500
.dark:bg-gray-700.dark:text-white
.bg-white.dark:bg-gray-700

/* Select multiple */
.w-full.px-3.py-2.border.border-gray-300.dark:border-gray-600.rounded-md.shadow-sm
.focus:outline-none.focus:ring-2.focus:ring-blue-500.focus:border-blue-500
.dark:bg-gray-700.dark:text-white
/* size="5" для видимых опций */

/* File input */
.w-full.px-3.py-2.border.border-gray-300.dark:border-gray-600.rounded-md.shadow-sm
.focus:outline-none.focus:ring-2.focus:ring-blue-500.focus:border-blue-500
.dark:bg-gray-700.dark:text-white

/* Disabled input */
.w-full.px-3.py-2.border.border-gray-300.dark:border-gray-600.rounded-md
.bg-gray-100.dark:bg-gray-700.text-gray-500.dark:text-gray-400
.cursor-not-allowed
```

### Checkbox
